1. connect the programmer 
2. find out the correct serial port
3. put the sensor in boot mode ( 1. press and hold cfg button 2. While holding cfg button, press and release the reset button 3. Release cfg button)
4. command to start the update "python ncd_py_bootloader.py <com port> <ncd update file>"
example -- python ncd_py_bootloader.py COM3 TYPE 80_V19_7FFF.bin

Make sure the python script and bin file are in same folder
